OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779901592
OL,3,CHundreds of university staff could
OL,4,Close jobs as part of proposed
OL,5,Crestructure
OL,7,FThe University of Sussex has warned
OL,8,Fthat a potential staffing restructure
OL,9,Fcould lead to the loss of up to 200
OL,10,Fjobs.
OL,12,FIn a statement, the university's Vice
OL,13,FChancellor, Professor Sasha Roseneil,
OL,14,Fapologised to staff and students for
OL,15,Fwhat she called a "regrettable
OL,16,Fsituation".
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
