PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779901592
OL,3,CHundreds of university staff could
OL,4,Close jobs as part of proposed
OL,5,Crestructure
OL,7,FShe said the job losses were part of a
OL,8,Fproposed reorganisation of its
OL,9,F"operations and academic delivery",
OL,10,Fwhich is hoped will save around #35
OL,11,Fmillion.
OL,13,FA consultation on the proposals will
OL,14,Fget underway tomorrow.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
