FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779901592
OL,3,CHundreds of university staff could
OL,4,Close jobs as part of proposed
OL,5,Crestructure
OL,7,FMs Roseneil said: "Like many
OL,8,Funiversities across the country, the
OL,9,FUniversity of Sussex is facing the
OL,10,Fcontinued need to make very difficult
OL,11,Fdecisions to address the impact of the
OL,12,Ffinancial sustainability crisis
OL,13,Faffecting UK higher education.
OL,15,F"This crisis results from the long-
OL,16,Fterm underfunding of teaching and
OL,17,Fresearch, ongoing inflationary
OL,18,Fpressures, and a steep fall in
OL,19,Finternational students driven by
OL,20,Fgovernment policy changes.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779901592
OL,3,CHundreds of university staff could
OL,4,Close jobs as part of proposed
OL,5,Crestructure
OL,7,F"Since 2023/24 Sussex has
OL,8,Fsignificantly reduced expenditure
OL,9,Fthrough non-pay savings, vacancy
OL,10,Fmanagement and cutting our capital
OL,11,Fprogramme, and 528 staff have left the
OL,12,Funiversity under two voluntary leavers
OL,13,Fschemes.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779901592
OL,3,CHundreds of university staff could
OL,4,Close jobs as part of proposed
OL,5,Crestructure
OL,7,F"Despite this, we still need to make
OL,8,Ffurther savings. That means we must
OL,9,Fnow strategically reorganise our
OL,10,Foperations and academic delivery to
OL,11,Fensure our longterm financial
OL,12,Fsustainability, making us more
OL,13,Feffective and efficient and enabling
OL,14,Fus to realise the long-term ambitions
OL,15,Flaid out in our strategy, Sussex 2035:
OL,16,FCreating Progressive Futures -
OL,17,Fflourishing, sustainability and
OL,18,Fprogress for the whole world.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779901592
OL,3,CHundreds of university staff could
OL,4,Close jobs as part of proposed
OL,5,Crestructure
OL,7,F"As the proposal to reorganise our
OL,8,Foperations and academic delivery may
OL,9,Fresult in the loss of approximately
OL,10,F200 (full time equivalent) roles
OL,11,Fthrough redundancy, we are now
OL,12,Fconsulting our recognised trade unions
OL,13,Fand our staff about this regrettable
OL,14,Fsituation.
OL,16,F"Sussex has a deeply committed
OL,17,Fcommunity of staff and students, and I
OL,18,Fam very sorry that we have not been
OL,19,Fable to avoid this announcement of job
OL,20,Flosses."
OL,26,@rD@EpmrD@Zpn
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
