PN,41307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779901592
OL,3,CHundreds of university staff could
OL,4,Close jobs as part of proposed
OL,5,Crestructure
OL,7,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FThe trade union UNISON has criticised
OL,13,Fthe announcement, saying any further
OL,14,Fjob losses will "add to the strain and
OL,15,Funcertainty facing colleagues left
OL,16,Fbehind, and lower morale".
OL,18,FA spokesperson said: "Staff have
OL,19,Falready endured wave after wave of
OL,20,Fcuts and uncertainty.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1779901592
OL,3,CHundreds of university staff could
OL,4,Close jobs as part of proposed
OL,5,Crestructure
OL,7,F"It's unacceptable to ask remaining
OL,8,Femployees to carry even heavier
OL,9,Fworkloads after hundreds of colleagues
OL,10,Fhave gone.
OL,12,F"Universities cannot cut their way to
OL,13,Fstability while expecting staff and
OL,14,Fstudents to pay the price.
OL,16,F"These proposals will cause huge
OL,17,Fanxiety across the higher education
OL,18,Fsector and the South East, and the
OL,19,Funion will do all it can to protect
OL,20,Fstaff and prevent job losses."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/9
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
